parent1.code: a watercolor of a green dragon flying in the style of traditional Chinese painting. It soars through clouds on the misty peaks in the ancient mountains on a foggy morning, breathing fire, with pagodas and cherry blossoms dotting the landscape.

offspring.code: A vibrant watercolor of a majestic emerald dragon gracefully soaring in the style of intricate traditional Chinese painting. It glides effortlessly through wispy, pearlescent clouds on the mist-shrouded, craggy peaks in the ancient, mystical mountains on a tranquil, foggy morning, breathing shimmering golden flames, with ornate pagodas and delicate pink cherry blossoms dotting the landscape.
